    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Lissodendoryx (Anomodoryx) oxychaetum (Menegola, Santos, Moraes & Muricy, 2012) comb. nov. A, specimen in situ (UFPEPOR 4291); B, cross section showing the choanosome and ectosome; Spicular set: C, Strongyles; D, oxychaetes; E, arcuate isochelae. Scales: B = 375 µm; C = 50 µm; D = 25 µm; E =12.5 µm." ;
